---
title: Mexican Beef & Veggie Taquitos with Corn Salsa & Cheddar Cheese
description: Taquitos are delightful because you can wrap them up with the tastiest filling cooked just the way you like it. We suggest wrapping these ones up with a spiced beef and veggie filling with an enchilada-based sauce. Every taquito needs a sprinkling of Cheddar cheese and a charred corn salsa.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mexican-beef-veggie-taquitos-7a3726d7.jpg
